profile:
*** FREE POOL REMOVAL Estimation + 10-year warranty on any sinking or settling that may occur ***

Blue2Green Group Ltd has been specializing in Swimming Pool Demolition and Removals since 1997.  We remove all types of pools including but not limited to concrete pools/gunite pools, vinyl liner pools, block pools, and in-ground pools, above ground pools.  

We also completely remove pools or do your standard fill-in. Vinyl Pools Removal, Concrete Pool Demolition / Gunite Pool Demolition, Block Pools 
Fibreglass Pools, Above Ground Pools Removal, Pool Demolition, Removal, Fill-In, Concrete Demolition & Removal, General Excavating, Natural Stone Retaining Walls

We service all over the greater Toronto (GTA) area and all surrounding areas including but not limited too:  
Ajax, Aurora, Brampton, Burlington, Etobicoke, Markham, Mississauga, Newmarket, North York, Oshawa, Pickering, Richmond Hill, Scarborough, Stouffville, Thornhill, Unionville, Whitby, Willowdale.

***

profile: At Master spas of Toronto, we have helped thousands of families escape their hectic lives. Whether by designing your perfect backyard outdoor oasis or your ultimate games room, let our knowledgeable staff provide solutions that will comfort and pamper you. We choose to offer our customers an unparalleled selection and value from a host of top brands which can be readily seen by visiting any of our Ontario warehouse showroom locations in Kitchener, Waterloo, Mississauga, Toronto or Barrie. With over 35 different spa models on display you will never have to buy from a picture. Buying wholesale direct gives our customers the best value and you can always rest assured that your purchase will be backed by the expertise and support of our service staff.
brands: Top hot tub and swim spa brands include award winning Master Spas, Twilight Series Spas and H2X Swim Spas.
payment_method: Payment methods that we can accept include Certified Bank Drafts, MasterCard, Visa, Amex and Cash

profile: K & E Pools has over 20 years experience working in the swimming pool industry, both residential and commercial.  We strive to deliver personalized service with quality and efficiency in the GTA.  We believe that no job is to small and pride ourselves in our ability to stay within our clients' budgets and deliver our services in a timely manner.  We are a fully insured company and look after every aspect of your pool and spa needs from pool resurfacing, tiling, skimmer installation, pressure test/sonar test, leak repair, liner installation, new equipment installation, deck repair, opening/closings, maintenance and much more. Visit our website to get a full list on all the services we can provide.
